      <div class="text">Late August, 2018 – open and operate 32 Know community</div>
      <div class="secondTitle">8.3 Financing Plan</div>
      <div class="text">July, 2018 – initiate the first private investment</div>
      <div class="text">Late July, 2018 – publish tokens</div>
      <div class="text">August, 2018 – launch on exchange</div>
      <div class="text">Late August, 2018 – initiate ICO</div>
      <div class="firstTitle">9. Core Team Members</div>
