      <div class="text">F2Pool and other mining firms seek business cooperation with 32 Know, expecting to increase users’ cohesion through our community.</div>
      <div class="firstTitle">11. Conclusion</div>
      <div class="text">32 Know combines the advantages of both blockchain and social media industries to tackle the challenges. As a pioneer, 32 Know adopts an unprecedent way to return users in China’s social media industry, that is, to provide exchangeable tokens to authors and readers. On 32 Know, individual return is correlated with their contribution. Based on the market price and fluidity of Zhili, our tokens will share value as legal tender, and Zhili possessors will be given more exclusive earning opportunities.</div>
